YEP in collaboration with Circle! 

We are delighted to announce the partnership of CIRCLE and YEP to join hands for #SheLovesTech Pakistan 2020. Yes, the world's largest startup competition for women entrepreneurs is back and it promises to be bigger than previous editions. 

We are combining forces to impact the economic future of Pakistan by investing in women. These dynamic women will bring their knowledge, skills, voice, ideas and imagination to an international platform to represent us globally. We know they will make us proud. 

Get your startups registered because Pakistan needs you to bring your ideas alive on a global stage.

The winner will receive the following incentives:
- Win cash prizes of 15,000 USD
- Participate in a high-level boot camp including workshops Designed to refine your businesses and
- Network with investors, leaders & entrepreneurs in the ecosystem
- Visit leading tech companies & incubators.

Are you excited? So, are we because we believe in you. Apply at the following link: https://apply.shelovestech.org/
